                                            Monthly Charges (Avg, Max, Min)

                                           BUSINESSS QUESTION
What is the average monthly charge across all customers? Also, what are the highest and lowest charges?

                              QUERIES
SELECT
    AVG(Monthly_Charge) AS avg_monthly_charge,
    MAX(Monthly_Charge) AS highest_monthly_charge,
    MIN(Monthly_Charge) AS lowest_monthly_charge
FROM telecom_customer

                                 
